的充电补能服务！」 「小米汽车携手小鹏汽车，正式开始充电补能网络合作。9000+ 小鹏充电桩入驻小米充电地图，支持在充电地图中实时查看小鹏充电场站的动态数据，同时支持小米汽车 App 扫码充电与即插即充服务，充电补能更高效！」 「小米汽车携手理想汽车，开启充电补能网络合作。6000+ 理想充电桩入驻小米充电地图，部分充电桩支持小米汽车 App 扫码充电，更多功能敬请期待！」 此前，雷军和王化都曾在社交媒体上透露，小米将与蔚来，小鹏，理想达成充电补能网络合作。 对此，网友纷纷表示雷总的朋友圈太强大，未来新能源车主充电更方便了。 小米官宣：与蔚来、小鹏、理想达成合作 _ 充电 _ 汽车 _ 网络"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d0988e8fba79162f3c489f926cee95c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7807982689"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIlpfYtNqemYIkEAMaCTExMjUzODE4OSDNkq67BjAAOJcBQB1yCjc4MDc5ODI2ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1855565631300194305", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/parker/campaign/1850589728451207169", "title": "知乎电子书 2024 年度书单公布！", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg1NTU2NTYzMTMwMDE5NDMwNXITMTg1NTU2NTYzMTMwMDE5NDMwNXgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1855565631300194305", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/parker/campaign/1850589728451207169", "title": "知乎电子书 2024 年度书单公布！", "source_type": 0, "attach